title: Sinéad O'Connor died of natural causes, coroner says
description: The Irish singer died on Jul. 26, 2023, at the age of 56. A tribute concert for O'Connor and Irish artist Shane MacGowan is planned for March in New York.

title: South Korea's parliament endorses landmark legislation outlawing dog meat industry
description: The bill would make the slaughtering, breeding, trade and sales of dog meat for human consumption illegal from 2027 and punish such acts with 2-3 years in prison.
